  ('disabled-e3452428-moex-00173', 'disabled-e3452428', 'disabled-e3452428-moex-112-3a7b2121', 'sub-disabled-e3452428-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者可做為衡量政府規模的指標之一？', '["人口數", "國土面積", "公務員人數", "國內生產毛額 30260"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c656bacef83f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d0b0b941c418", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "301", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "行政學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "一般民政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-e3452428-moex-00174', 'disabled-e3452428', 'disabled-e3452428-moex-112-3a7b2121', 'sub-disabled-e3452428-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者是「新公共行政」與「黑堡宣言」的共同點？', '["重視行政人員的角色", "推崇科學管理的精神", "主張自由放任的思想", "支持政治與行政分立"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c656bacef83f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d0b0b941c418", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "301", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "行政學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "一般民政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-e3452428-moex-00175', 'disabled-e3452428', 'disabled-e3452428-moex-112-3a7b2121', 'sub-disabled-e3452428-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於賽蒙（H.Simon）決策理論的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["所謂行政行為，就是組織中決策制定的整個過程", "全面瞭解及解決行政問題，必須同時注重決定與執行", "組織目標的達成，是由基層執行人員與高層決策者共同配合的結果", "探討高層決策者所做決定，即能完整瞭解組織的運作及影響"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c656bacef83f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d0b0b941c418", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "301", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "行政學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "一般民政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-e3452428-moex-00176', 'disabled-e3452428', 'disabled-e3452428-moex-112-3a7b2121', 'sub-disabled-e3452428-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關政府再造（reinventinggovernment）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["以企業型政府的觀念引導政府改造方向", "政府機關的運作完全比照私人企業", "政府應由具備創新精神的官僚來管理", "行政人員要能夠察覺並快速回應公眾的需求"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c656bacef83f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d0b0b941c418", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "301", "s": "0603", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "行政學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "一般民政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
